{"tid":2331571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暖氣軍師撐香港對英國藍絲予以堅決還擊 推廣英國黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2020-12-19T01:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T17:43:37.000Z","uid":1799,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"96c1c1523715f5486f97de157584d5aca583fff1","tid":2331571,"uid":1799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"曼市華埠街坊商會前會長陳新貴於Facebook無的放矢，抹黑於12月12號嘅合法和平集會，此舉動嚴重干涉了英國內政，是赤裸裸的霸權行徑，暖氣軍師撐香港堅決反對。中大理大守衛戰一周年悼念集會，事先有依法向警方申請，當時有英國警方在場觀察。中方制裁澳洲導致中國人民缺煤停電，陳新貴不顧祖國同胞飽受霜寒之苦，反而關心在英港人嘅集會權益，無不暴露著紅色勢力插手英國內政的卑劣行徑，更意圖組織群眾「去對應呢班人」，其背後讓紅色勢力滲透英國的政治圖謀早已是&ldquo;司馬昭之心&rdquo;，每一個人都應看清這樣的險惡用心！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYfTvUU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYfTvUU.png&h=037f2eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳新貴講嘅係廣東話，於1966年前倚仗英國政府施恩得以移民英國，係祖國同胞受文化大革命煎熬嘅同時，自己則享受民主自由帶黎嘅經濟繁榮。如今竟打壓港人合法權益、干涉英國內政，如此背宗忘祖嘅行為，必會牢牢地釘在歷史的恥辱柱上！<br />\n<br />\n陳新貴於接受D100訪問時堅稱抹黑抗爭者為「亂港廢青」係冇問題，其一錯再錯，死不悔改嘅態度已引致眾叛親離，包括英國創城地產嘅割席，此舉只係拿石頭砸自己的腳，燃點每一個人於英國推行黃色經濟圈嘅意志。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLeH8Gx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLeH8Gx.png&h=638d9d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前，對抗暴政、光復香港乃大勢所趨、民心所向，陳新貴及曼市華埠街坊商會del左post就裝聾作啞，意欲何為？是擔心藏不住自己做的腌臢事，還是怕惹怒未來數十萬計以BNO5+1計劃移民英國嘅香港人，從此丟了「賣港賺錢」的路子？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1r2KCFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1r2KCFw.png&h=b7b9b85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參與討論 / Forum<br />\nTG公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/justitiahongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjustitiahongkong&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=05b3234b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/justitiahongkong</a><br />\nTG Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/BoilerTacticians\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBoilerTacticians&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=bc329cf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BoilerTacticians</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/justitiahk?igshid=9eheab7n4pkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjustitiahk%3Figshid%3D9eheab7n4pkw&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=369e4f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/justitiahk?igshid=9eheab7n4pkw</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JustitiaHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJustitiaHK%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f470f3f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JustitiaHK/</a><br />\n課金支持 / Support Us<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/hmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by5stzhWLkAbKoDyPhYMXi6ebKcGJ1G6YvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by5stzhWLkAbKoDyPhYMXi6ebKcGJ1G6YvY&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=be453c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/hmbnxs-justice-for-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3qibQNkZ06RutUJ4vRmrI1by5stzhWLkAbKoDyPhYMXi6ebKcGJ1G6YvY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JT9O5q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JT9O5q.png&h=30c94d9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3f8b5154dabcaa3aaefe97a008d9b81fe8ebe7b","tid":2331571,"uid":1799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2330934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2330934/page/1</a><br />\n[注意] 英國藍地產, youtuber, 商鋪 - 唔好比錢佢地賺"},{"pid":"f8107d9a3901315f3e478ad827c367c270f19f52","tid":2331571,"uid":109428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51aecfee793add2200d30b4c370af09c52c55c49","tid":2331571,"uid":258696,"like":0